         <div type="translation">
            <p><choice corresp="#a2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>333</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1997"/><citedRange>114</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... from all Saṃsāra sufferings right down to the Avīci-hell ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a3"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>289, 294</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:hackstein1995"/><citedRange>175</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a4"><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... by the power and compassion [that comes] out of our own self ...</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>124, 404</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>745</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">In (eben diesem) Augenblick kam in deiner [Geburten]folge der Same der Buddhaschaft, würdig, von Göttern [und] Menschen auf dem Scheitel getragen zu werden, zum Vorschein.</seg><seg type="sec_transl" resp="TI">At (this very) moment, there appeared in your sequence [of incarnations] the seed of Buddhahood, worthy of being worn on the crown of the head by gods [and] humans.</seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:schmidtkt1974"/><citedRange>366</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#a6"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1997"/><citedRange>137</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b1"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1957"/><citedRange>240</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b2"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>738</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b4"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:carling2000"/><citedRange>287</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1952"/><citedRange>36</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>741</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><seg type="prim_transl">... Am I able to be a protection for these beings or am I not able to?</seg></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b5"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1952"/><citedRange>37</citedRange></bibl></seg><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:thomas1954"/><citedRange>741</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice><choice corresp="#b6"><seg><bibl><title corresp="ref:hackstein1995"/><citedRange>296</citedRange></bibl></seg></choice></p>
